644
00:55:48,578 --> 00:55:51,982
Told me the cops
are our enemies.

645
00:55:52,449 --> 00:55:56,218
And, uh, you know,
they're just pigs.

646
00:55:57,620 --> 00:56:02,625
Descendants from slave owners
